Subject: VM patched for vulnerability but when it came up, the IP was missing
Description:
Our VM team had to apply a patch to patch out a vulnerability in the VM running our EPP server and after applying the patch, the VM came up but the IP settings were missing. We're trying to define it but its not accepting it, failing with an error "Invalid gateway".

So we're unable to get the Appliance up and running again. Please assist as this is quite urgent
